{"base_path":"/","components":null,"consumes":"[\"application/json;charset=UTF-8\",\"application/json\"]","definitions":{"AttachServerVolumeRequest":{"description":"Lite Server服务器挂载磁盘ID","properties":{"volume_id":{"description":"**参数解释**:待挂载磁盘的磁盘ID。\n**约束限制**:不涉及。\n**取值范围**:^[0-9a-f]{8}-[0-9a-f]{4}-[1-5][0-9a-f]{3}-[89ab][0-9a-f]{3}-[0-9a-f]{12}$。 \n**默认取值**:不涉及。","example":"1e79eff7-c02b-4dfd-a0d6-f76c90d9b4e0","type":"string"}},"required":["volume_id"],"type":"object"},"AttachServerVolumeResponse":{"properties":{"operation_id":{"description":"**参数解释**:操作ID。 \n**取值范围**:^[0-9a-f]{8}-[0-9a-f]{4}-[1-5][0-9a-f]{3}-[89ab][0-9a-f]{3}-[0-9a-f]{12}$。","type":"string"},"operation_status":{"description":"**参数解释**:操作状态。 \n**取值范围**:\n- pending 等待处理\n- running 运行中\n- success 成功\n- failed 失败","type":"string"},"operation_type":{"description":"**参数解释**:操作类型。\n**取值范围**:node_attach_volume","type":"string"}},"type":"object"}},"description":null,"group_id":"ade740e866904a7dbdaa5ec0f538d4d0","host":"modelarts.cn-north-4.myhuaweicloud.com","id":"126257bbdbc64fb7856f946799783ff2","info_version":"v1","method":"post","name":"AttachDevServerVolume","parameters":{"projectId":{"description":"用户项目ID。获取方法请参见[获取项目ID和名称](modelarts_03_0147.xml)。","in":"path","name":"project_id","required":true,"type":"string"}},"paths":{"/v1/{project_id}/dev-servers/{id}/attachvolume":{"post":{"description":"Lite Server服务器挂载磁盘接口用于将额外的磁盘挂载到Lite Server服务器上。该接口适用于以下场景:当用户需要扩展Lite Server服务器的存储空间以满足更大的数据存储需求时,可以通过此接口将指定的磁盘挂载到服务器上。使用该接口的前提条件是Lite Server服务器已创建且处于运行状态、或者停止状态,用户具有挂载磁盘的权限,且指定的磁盘已存在且未被其他服务器使用。挂载操作完成后,磁盘将成功挂载到Lite Server服务器上,用户可以访问和使用新增的存储空间。若Lite Server服务器不存在、指定的磁盘不存在或已被使用,或用户无权限操作,接口将返回相应的错误信息。","operationId":"AttachDevServerVolume","parameters":[{"description":"**参数解释**:Lite Server实例ID。 \n**约束限制**:不涉及。 \n**取值范围**:^[0-9a-f]{8}-[0-9a-f]{4}-[1-5][0-9a-f]{3}-[89ab][0-9a-f]{3}-[0-9a-f]{12}$。\n**默认取值**:不涉及。","in":"path","name":"id","required":true,"type":"string"},{"$ref":"#/parameters/projectId"},{"description":"**参数解释**:DevServer服务器挂载磁盘请求体。","in":"body","name":"AttachDevServerVolumeRequestBody","required":true,"schema":{"$ref":"#/definitions/AttachServerVolumeRequest"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"OK。","examples":{"application/json":{"operation_id":"b894b879-a3c0-49ee-b5cb-92202b2794e2","operation_status":"pending","operation_type":"node_attach_volume"}},"headers":{"X-Request-Id":{"description":"链路追踪编号","type":"string"}},"schema":{"$ref":"#/definitions/AttachServerVolumeResponse"}}},"summary":"Lite Server服务器挂载磁盘","tags":["Lite Server管理"],"x-api-type":"open-api","x-apiexplorer-hide":"N","x-constraint":"仅限A3。","x-is-registered":"Y","x-open-region-cloud":"hk,hc","x-order":24,"x-publish-doc":"Y","x-request-examples-1":{"volume_id":"1e79eff7-c02b-4dfd-a0d6-f76c90d9b4e0"},"x-request-examples-text-1":{"volume_id":"1e79eff7-c02b-4dfd-a0d6-f76c90d9b4e0"},"x-request-examples-url-1":"POST https://{endpoint}/v1/{project_id}/dev-servers/{id}/attachvolume","x-support-sdk":"N"}}},"product_short":"ModelArts","region_id":"cn-north-4","schemes":["HTTPS"],"security_definitions":{"ApiTokenAuth":{"in":"header","name":"X-Auth-Token","type":"apiKey"}},"summary":"Lite Server服务器挂载磁盘","tags":"Lite Server管理","uri":null,"version":"2.0"}